OL,5, The boss of British Gas owner Centrica 
OL,6, has refused to be drawn on whether he  
OL,7, will take a bonus worth up to #1.6m    
OL,8, after the company posted huge profits. 
OL,10,FChris O'Shea said it was "too early to 
OL,11,Fhave a conversation" over any payout   
OL,12,Fafter profits hit #3.3bn for 2022.     
OL,14,FEnergy firms have seen record profits  
OL,15,Fsince oil and gas prices jumped        
OL,16,Ffollowing Russia's invasion of Ukraine.
OL,18,FIt has sparked calls for firms to pay  
OL,19,Fmore tax as many households being hit  
OL,20,Fby high gas and electricity bills.     
